Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.03,0:00:17.53,Main,Speedwagon,0,0,0,,Jo{\fscx300}-{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.53,0:00:19.04,Main,Will A. Zeppeli,0,0,0,,Jojo!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.04,0:00:20.58,Main,Poco,0,0,0,,H-He did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.26,0:00:22.08,Main,Jonathan,0,0,0,,This isn't over!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.58,0:00:28.20,Main,Jonathan,0,0,0,,I never expected he would reach the surface at the same speed as the Ripple...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.20,0:00:32.81,Main,Jonathan,0,0,0,,What speed... The Overdrive only grazed Bruford's forehead!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.51,0:00:38.64,Main,Jonathan,0,0,0,,It looks like I'll have to deliver the Ripple of the sun with a full-contact punch after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.34,0:00:48.15,Main,Bruford,0,0,0,,Master Dio! I offer my eternal gratitude for being revived, \Nas well as the chance to fight this child! {Jesus this is a mouthful.}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.62,0:00:51.79,Main,Bruford,0,0,0,,He is worthy to bear the title of a true warrior!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.79,0:00:55.98,Main,Bruford,0,0,0,,We shall no longer hold ourselves back within the confines of underwater battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.98,0:01:00.49,Main,Bruford,0,0,0,,Let this be a battle of strength versus strength! \NSkill versus skill! Cunning versus cunning!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.49,0:01:05.92,Main,Bruford,0,0,0,,You whelp! Prove that you can stand up in battle against the mighty Bruford!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.92,0:01:08.21,Main,Bruford,0,0,0,,Wrryyyyyy!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.21,0:01:12.01,Main,Jonathan,0,0,0,,Even under Dio's influence, he still has the same pride he had until the day he died!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.01,0:01:15.85,Main,Jonathan,0,0,0,,And that pride is rooted in his respect for intense battling!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.85,0:01:18.93,Main,Bruford,0,0,0,,I'll take your blood and make it my own!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.93,0:01:20.94,Main,Jonathan,0,0,0,,He's attacking with his hair again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.94,0:01:24.06,Main,Jonathan,0,0,0,,Have at it! This time I'll send my Ripple right through it!
